## §A.1 Invariant lattice (n=6)

```
σ(6) · φ(6) = n · τ(6) = J₂ = 24
   12   ·   2  =  6  ·   4  = 24
sopfr(6) = 2 + 3 = 5      μ(6) = 1      λ(6) = 2 (Liouville)
σ - φ = 10                σ² = 144      σ³ = 1728      n^τ = 6⁴ = 1296
```

| Symbol  | Value | Role                       | post-aural BCI projection |
|---------|------:|----------------------------|---------------------------|
| n       | 6     | master row                 | 6 cortical pyramidal layers (neocortex) — 6-phase synaptic pattern |
| σ(6)    | 12    | sigma — sum-of-divisors    | 12 cortical target zones (A1·A2·V1·V2·V4·V5·V6·S1·S2·M1·PFC·hippocampal-relay); 12 ch / micro-tile |
| τ(6)    | 4     | tau — divisor count        | 4 operating modes (sense / inject / sync / sleep); 4 cortex layers tapped (II/III · IV · V · VI) |
| φ(6)    | 2     | phi — Euler totient        | 2 clips (left + right mastoid); φ=2 bidirectional (read + write) per channel |
| sopfr(6)| 5     | sum of prime factors 2+3   | ≤ 5 mm temporal-bone thickness window; ≤ 5 ms closed-loop decode latency |
| μ(6)    | 1     | Möbius                     | 1 μm nano-coil litho pitch; 1 % (μ=1) seizure-watchdog false-alarm floor |
| λ(6)    | 2     | Liouville                  | 2 redundancy channels per safety-critical lane |
| J₂      | 24    | Mathieu / Leech min-vector | 24 bidirectional channels / macro-tile; σ·φ = n·τ = J₂; 24-year (φ·σ) coating lifetime |
| σ - φ   | 10    | benchtop-cm / 10× scale    | ≈ 10 g total clip-pair mass; 10× → 1 (18 wearables 한 자릿수로 수렴) |
| σ²      | 144   | throughput multiplier      | 144 channels / tile; σ²·σ⁴·... = 1.44 M ch full-head array |
| σ³      | 1728  | volume multiplier          | 1728-electrode-equivalent virtual array (σ³ · ... ); Neuralink 1024 → σ³ |
| n^τ     | 1296  | 6⁴ hex lattice             | 1296-ch hexagonal cortical-column lattice (Neuralink 1024 ch parity·+) |

Authority: this file §A.1 is the SSOT; every pillar doc + verify/* re-asserts these.

