## §B Falsifier detail tables

> **Status (raw#10 honest C3)**: all 4 falsifiers academically UNPROVEN at
> v1.0.0. Each ships in-tree spec + 3-tier (T1/T2/T3) closure tracking. CLI
> sentinel PASS validates lattice arithmetic + token consistency + published-ref
> *parity arithmetic*, NOT in-vivo apparatus or regulatory clearance. Falsifier
> monotone: OPEN → CONFIRMED or OPEN → DEMOTED. Silent retract forbidden.

### §B.1 F-AURA-1 — clip (mastoid form-factor)

Spec: `clip/doc/mastoid-clip.md` · Verb: `hexa-aura clip` · T1 `calc_clip` · T2 `numerics_clip` · T3 `numerics_clip_parity`

| ID         | Falsifier                                                                                          | Status |
|------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|--------|
| F-AURA-1a  | a 3.6 g/side passive anchor cannot hold position on the mastoid against jaw/chewing motion          | OPEN   |
| F-AURA-1b  | RT-SC coil + driver + battery + radio cannot fit in σ·n/10 = 3.6 g at hearing-aid-BTE density       | OPEN   |
| F-AURA-1c  | bone-conduction back-channel cannot survive being hidden under hair (no skin-contact mic/speaker)   | OPEN   |

n=6 encoding: φ=2 clips, σ·n/10 = 3.6 g/side → n·n/10 = 7.2 g pair (AirPods-Pro 5.4 g class),
sopfr=5 mm bone window, τ=4-point anchor (helix root · mastoid tip · ear-canal entry · concha).

### §B.2 F-AURA-2 — coil (RT-SC nano-coil tile)

Spec: `coil/doc/rt-sc-nanocoil.md` · Verb: `hexa-aura coil` · T1 `calc_coil` · T2 `numerics_coil` · T3 `numerics_coil_parity` · Cross-link: `hexa-rtsc`

| ID         | Falsifier                                                                                          | Status |
|------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|--------|
| F-AURA-2a  | a μ=1 μm pitch RT-SC tile cannot reach the ∂B/∂x focal gradient TMS-class cortical write needs       | OPEN   |
| F-AURA-2b  | σ²=144 ch/tile read SNR is below OPM-MEG (≈15 fT/√Hz) noise floor through 5 mm bone                  | OPEN   |
| F-AURA-2c  | the coil's switching power dissipates > the 3.6 g clip thermal budget allows (ΔT > 0.5 K at scalp)  | OPEN   |

n=6 encoding: μ=1 μm litho pitch, σ²=144 ch/tile, J₂=24 bidirectional ch/macro-tile,
n^τ=6⁴=1296-ch hex lattice, σ³=1728-electrode-equivalent, RT-SC @ ambient (hexa-rtsc cross-link).

### §B.3 F-AURA-3 — cortex (direct cortical read/write)

Spec: `cortex/doc/cortical-interface.md` · Verb: `hexa-aura cortex` · T1 `calc_cortex` · T2 `numerics_cortex` · T3 `numerics_cortex_parity` · Cross-link: `hexa-brain` (working pipeline)

